==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhook
<hw>Un*hook"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>hook</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from a hook; to
undo or open by loosening or unfastening the hooks of; <as>as, to
<ex>unhook</ex> a fish; to <ex>unhook</ex> a dress</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

